        "paragraph_index": 2,
        "text": "### 2. Limitations Regarding Your Conditions\n\nRegarding the specific conditions you mentioned:\n\n| Condition | Your Request | SRD-46 Coverage |\n|-----------|-------------|-----------------|\n| **Temperature** | 200 °C | Most data is at 25 °C; some high-temperature data exists but 200 °C entries are rare |\n| **Pressure** | 50 bar | Pressure is **not** a standard recorded parameter in SRD-46 |\n\nSRD-46 primarily catalogs stability constants measured under conventional aqueous conditions (typically 25 °C, ambient pressure, with specified ionic strength and electrolyte medium). While some measurements at elevated temperatures do exist in the database, **pressure is not explicitly tracked** as a condition variable.",
